In re S.S. 2018-0686 Supreme Court of Ohio. May 17, 2018

CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS

MOTION AND PROCEDURAL RULINGS

Sua sponte, case ordered to proceed according to the Rules of Practice of the Supreme Court of Ohio that pertain to cases involving termination of parental rights. Appellee's memorandum in response shall be filed within 20 days.
